if we use just classes, our classes will so coupled (depend on each others)
Interface created to remove these coupling
if a class1 need class2 obj,
we create a filed on class1 based on class2 obj type as "dependency" on class2.
we create class2 obj on main and inject it to class1 as "dependency injection"

Note: in framework like Spring
      in Service & Controller classes that needs other class obj (depend on them)
      Spring will inject dependencies automatically (by Beans)

